            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Ah yes, this is an intentional change. `vim.lsp.Client` now has its own reference to every field in `vim.lsp.ClientConfig` so overwriting the reference at `client.config.settings` will no longer work, instead you should change `client.settings` (which is initialised to the reference pointed to by `client.config.settings`).\r\n\r\nRef https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/27443",
